data.description:
Welcome to 1508 Vanderlip Dr, Gastonia NC – a diamond in the rough awaiting your personal touch! This charming 3 bed 2.5 bath tri level home offers endless potential and is ready for your creative vision to bring it back to its former glory. With a little TLC, this property can become the perfect canvas for your dream home.

Outside, the expansive backyard oasis awaits, offering the perfect backdrop for outdoor gatherings or simply unwinding after a long day. Imagine sipping cocktails on the patio as the sun sets behind the lush landscaping, creating a tranquil ambiance that's all your own.

Conveniently located near shopping, dining, and major highways, this home offers the best of both worlds – a peaceful retreat from the hustle and bustle, yet just minutes away from everything Gastonia has to offer.

Don't miss out on this incredible opportunity – schedule a showing today and unlock the possibilities at 1508 Vanderlip Dr!
